UI ko bright aur clean look dene ke liye humne dark mode se shift hokar **"Glassmorphism"** aur **"Soft Grey/White"** theme implement ki hai. Yeh design ab professional coding environment jaisa lagega.

### Changes:
1. **Light/Bright Theme:** Background ko soft grey/off-white (`#f4f7f6`) rakha hai.
2. **Card Design:** Card ko clean white (`rgba(255,255,255,0.9)`) aur soft shadow ke saath upgrade kiya hai.
3. **Syntax Highlighting:** Light background par code readable ho, isliye colors ko thoda dark aur contrasty rakha hai.
4. **Font:** JetBrains Mono ko maintain kiya hai kyunki yeh reading ke liye best hai.

